<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>战区</title><link>https://www.twz.com</link><description>防御世界的强大进攻。</description><lastBuildDate>Fri, 17 Apr 2026 02:34:54 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>乌克兰证明廉价拦截无人机可保护美军免受伊朗沙赫德袭击</title><link>https://www.twz.com/land/cheap-interceptor-drones-proven-in-ukraine-protected-u-s-troops-against-iranian-shaheds</link><description>&lt;p&gt;陆军高级官员赞扬了 Merops 无人机在防御伊朗远程神风特攻队无人机方面的表现。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/land/cheap-interceptor-drones-proven-in-ukraine-protected-u-s-troops-against-iranian-shaheds"&gt;乌克兰证明廉价拦截无人机保护美军免受伊朗沙赫德袭击的&lt;/a&gt;帖子首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;战区&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 16 Apr 2026 23:22:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/land/cheap-interceptor-drones-proven-in-ukraine-protected-u-s-troops-against-iranian-shaheds</guid></item><item><title>除了封锁之外，美国还在世界各地追捕与伊朗有关的船只（更新）</title><link>https://www.twz.com/news-features/u-s-pursuing-iranian-linked-ships-all-over-the-world-as-part-of-its-blockade</link><description>&lt;p&gt;参谋长联席会议主席表示，美国现在正在全球范围内努力追捕与支持伊朗有关的船只。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/news-features/u-s-pursuing-iranian-linked-ships-all-over-the-world-as-part-of-its-blockade"&gt;美国除封锁外还在世界各地追捕与伊朗有关的船只（更新）&lt;/a&gt;一文首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;战区&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 16 Apr 2026 22:55:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/news-features/u-s-pursuing-iranian-linked-ships-all-over-the-world-as-part-of-its-blockade</guid></item><item><title>适应性超强的 Mayhem 10 蜂群无人机由 Switchblade 演变而来</title><link>https://www.twz.com/air/super-adaptable-mayhem-10-swarming-drone-evolved-from-the-switchblade</link><description>&lt;p&gt;AeroVironment 的 Mayhem 10 是高度模块化的，可以搜索并摧毁敌方雷达、干扰通信、侦察机、攻击装甲等。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/air/super-adaptable-mayhem-10-swarming-drone-evolved-from-the-switchblade"&gt;由弹簧刀演变而来的超级适应性混乱 10 蜂群无人机&lt;/a&gt;首次出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;《战区》&lt;/a&gt;中。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 16 Apr 2026 21:15:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/air/super-adaptable-mayhem-10-swarming-drone-evolved-from-the-switchblade</guid></item><item><title>陆军关注无人机加油机为其新型 MV-75 Cheyenne II 倾转旋翼机加油</title><link>https://www.twz.com/air/army-eyes-drone-tankers-to-refuel-its-new-mv-75-cheyenne-ii-tiltrotors</link><description>&lt;p&gt;陆军和贝尔公司以美国海军的 MQ-25 Stingray 无人机加油机为例，展示了即将推出的产品。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/air/army-eyes-drone-tankers-to-refuel-its-new-mv-75-cheyenne-ii-tiltrotors"&gt;陆军注视无人机加油机为其新型 MV-75 Cheyenne II 倾转旋翼机加油&lt;/a&gt;首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;战区&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 16 Apr 2026 18:48:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/air/army-eyes-drone-tankers-to-refuel-its-new-mv-75-cheyenne-ii-tiltrotors</guid></item><item><title>AH-64阿帕奇新型反无人机炮弹弹药的生产正在加速</title><link>https://www.twz.com/air/production-of-ah-64-apaches-new-counter-drone-cannon-shell-ammunition-ramping-up</link><description>&lt;p&gt;陆军预计 XM1225 APEX 弹药的采购量将增加五倍。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/air/production-of-ah-64-apaches-new-counter-drone-cannon-shell-ammunition-ramping-up"&gt;AH-64 阿帕奇新型反无人机炮弹弹药的后期制作&lt;/a&gt;首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;《战区》&lt;/a&gt;中。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 16 Apr 2026 17:51:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/air/production-of-ah-64-apaches-new-counter-drone-cannon-shell-ammunition-ramping-up</guid></item><item><title>Wolf Pack 模块化迷你巡航导弹为阿帕奇和黑鹰推出</title><link>https://www.twz.com/air/wolf-pack-modular-mini-cruise-missiles-pitched-for-apache-black-hawk</link><description>&lt;p&gt;L3Harris 已经为海军陆战队建造了发射效果飞行器，现在希望将这些功能引入美国陆军旋翼机。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/air/wolf-pack-modular-mini-cruise-missiles-pitched-for-apache-black-hawk"&gt;为阿帕奇、黑鹰推出的“狼群”模块化迷你巡航导弹&lt;/a&gt;首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;“战区”&lt;/a&gt;上。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 16 Apr 2026 16:09:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/air/wolf-pack-modular-mini-cruise-missiles-pitched-for-apache-black-hawk</guid></item><item><title>初看暗夜魔王 MV-75 夏安 (Cheyenne) 的样子</title><link>https://www.twz.com/air/first-look-at-what-a-night-stalker-mv-75-cheyenne-will-look-like</link><description>&lt;p&gt;新的渲染图显示了 MV-75 具有特殊操作特定功能，如雷达、其他传感器和空中加油能力。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;帖子 &lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/air/first-look-at-what-a-night-stalker-mv-75-cheyenne-will-look-like"&gt;《初看夜行者 MV-75 夏安会是什么样子》&lt;/a&gt;首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;《战区》&lt;/a&gt;上。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 15 Apr 2026 23:19:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/air/first-look-at-what-a-night-stalker-mv-75-cheyenne-will-look-like</guid></item><item><title>特朗普淡化了中国对伊朗战争对其石油供应影响的担忧（更新）</title><link>https://www.twz.com/news-features/trump-downplays-chinese-concerns-over-iran-wars-impact-on-its-oil-supplies</link><description>&lt;p&gt;美国和中国之间因伊朗战争造成的能源运输中断而产生的摩擦仍然是一个主要问题。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/news-features/trump-downplays-chinese-concerns-over-iran-wars-impact-on-its-oil-supplies"&gt;特朗普淡化中国对伊朗战争对其石油供应影响的担忧（更新）&lt;/a&gt;首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;《战区》&lt;/a&gt;上。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 15 Apr 2026 20:28:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/news-features/trump-downplays-chinese-concerns-over-iran-wars-impact-on-its-oil-supplies</guid></item><item><title>德国现在正在空投其微型 Wiesel“Tankettes”</title><link>https://www.twz.com/land/germany-is-now-airdropping-its-tiny-wiesel-tankettes</link><description>&lt;p&gt;威塞尔以其敏捷性和小尺寸而闻名，从 A400M 运输机上卸下威塞尔为德国空降部队提供了一种快速向前部署火力的新方法。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/land/germany-is-now-airdropping-its-tiny-wiesel-tankettes"&gt;德国正在空投其微型威塞尔“坦克”&lt;/a&gt;一文首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;战区&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 15 Apr 2026 20:26:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/land/germany-is-now-airdropping-its-tiny-wiesel-tankettes</guid></item><item><title>CH-47 奇努克空射无人机群被誉为未来的特色</title><link>https://www.twz.com/air/ch-47-chinook-air-launching-swarms-of-drones-touted-as-future-feature</link><description>&lt;p&gt;波音公司还发现人们对“支奴干”的最佳载人版本越来越感兴趣。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;号称&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/air/ch-47-chinook-air-launching-swarms-of-drones-touted-as-future-feature"&gt;未来特色的 CH-47 支奴干空射无人机群&lt;/a&gt;首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;《战区》&lt;/a&gt;中。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 15 Apr 2026 18:26:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/air/ch-47-chinook-air-launching-swarms-of-drones-touted-as-future-feature</guid></item></channel></rss>